## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tafamidis Vyndaqel/Vyndamax 2019** = first FDA ATTR-CM mortality reduction (ATTR-ACT trial). TTR tetramer stabilization 이 cardiomyopathy-modifying 첫 입증. quantum-VQE 의 TTR pocket scaffold 가 직접 fit.
2. **acoramidis Attruby 2024** = first AG-10 small-molecule 2nd-gen TTR stabilizer (BridgeBio ATTRibute-CM). tafamidis 대비 broader variant + ATTRwt coverage. quantum-VQE 의 next-gen pocket leverage.
3. **patisiran Onpattro 2018 + vutrisiran Amvuttra 2022 + HELIOS-B 2024** = TTR siRNA polyneuropathy → ATTR-CM cardio expansion. LNP (patisiran) → GalNAc (vutrisiran) delivery 진화. quantum-VQE 의 RNA-target modulation 보조.
4. **inotersen Tegsedi 2018 + eplontersen Wainua 2023** = TTR ASO polyneuropathy → ATTR-CM trial. 1st-gen platelet 부작용 → 2nd-gen GalNAc 안전성 향상.
5. **NTLA-2001 (Intellia) ATTR Phase 3 MAGNITUDE** = first in-vivo CRISPR clinical in TTR. 단일 IV LNP-CRISPR 가 TTR knockdown lifelong (cross-gene_therapy_platform).
6. **daratumumab Darzalex AL 2021 (ANDROMEDA)** = first FDA AL amyloidosis (CyBorD + dara). plasma cell directed monoclonal anti-CD38 가 AL 첫 monoclonal targeted.
7. **CyBorD (cyclophosphamide + bortezomib + dex) classical** = AL classical regimen. PI + alkylator + corticosteroid combination 이 plasma cell + light chain reduction 표준.
8. **99mTc-PYP/HMDP scintigraphy** = ATTR-CM 진단 표준 (cross-theranostic). non-invasive ATTR vs AL 감별 + biopsy 회피.
9. **한국 K-amyloidosis 임상 + 식약처** = Korean V30M + V122I (African-American 4% 원래) variant 식별 (cross-pharmacogenomics + k_pharma_industry).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, cardiac amyloidosis 임상 의미 한정.

